quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,23,"Nnipa no bi wͻ agyidiefoͻ no mu a wͻdi nokorε wͻ apam a wͻ ne Nyankopͻn apam no ho. Ebinom nso wͻ hͻ a wͻadi wͻn bͻhyε no so (awu sε mogya ho adansefoͻ), na ebi nom nso wͻ hͻ a wͻretwεn, na wͻnsesaa (wͻn adwen wͻ bͻhyε) no ho koraa."
  33,24,"Sεdeε Nyankopͻn bɛtua nokorεfoͻ no nokorεdie no so ka, na sε Ɔpε a Watwe nkͻnkͻnsafoͻ no aso, anaasε Ɔde bεkyε wͻn. Nokorε sε Nyankopͻn ne Bͻnefakyε Hene, Ɔne Mmɔborɔhunufoɔ Hene."
  33,25,"Boniayεfoͻ no abufuhyeε no mu no, Nyankopͻn atwe wͻn asan akyire; wͻannya mfasoͻ biara wͻ so. Nyankopͻn som bo ma agyidiefoͻ no wͻ ͻkoo mu. Nyankopͻn ne Ɔhoͻdenfoͻ na Ɔne Otumfoͻ a Otumi ade nyinaa yε."
  33,26,"Nyamesom ho Nwomanimfoͻ a wͻboaa (atamfoͻ) no, Nyankopͻn sianee wͻn firii wͻn aban denden no so, na Ɔbͻͻ huu guu wͻn akoma mu; mokum ebinom na mofaa ebinom nso nnomum."
  33,27,"(Nyankopͻn) maa motenaa wͻn anan mu wͻ wͻn nsaase so, ne wͻn afie mu, ne wͻn agyapadeε ne nsaase a mo nan nsii so da so. Nyankopͻn na Ɔwͻ biribiara so tumi."
  33,28,"Nkͻmhyεni, ka kyerε w'ayerenom sε: “Sε mopε wiase asetena ne emu afεεfεdeε a, εneε mommra na mensum mo, na mama moakͻ no wͻ kwanpa so."
  33,29,"Na mmom sε mopε Nyankopͻn ne Ne somafoͻ no ne Daakye asetena (pa) no nso a, εneε Nyankopͻn asiesie akatua a εsom bo paa ama mo mu apapafoͻ no”."
  33,30,"Nkͻmhyεni ayerenom, mo mu nea ͻbɛyi suban bͻne bi adie no, yεde asotwee no bεbͻ ho mmmienu ama no. Ԑno deε εyε adeε a εyε mmrε ma Nyankopͻn."
